{"tid":2148301,"cid":38,"subCid":0,"title":"[花生] 英文維基百科動議禁絕黨媒","createTime":"2020-08-10T00:42:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-10T03:20:29.000Z","uid":363335,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b97f60fe7883bd18d575ccc69aca6f3486872465","tid":2148301,"uid":363335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T00:42:19.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\">大家可能知道維基百科嘅內容需要引用「可靠來源」。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n乜嘢係維基百科嘅<strong>「可靠來源」</strong>？原來維基百科有一大個表，列舉常見嘅新聞網站有幾可靠。<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedia:RSP\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FWikipedia%3ARSP&d=V6cANorTbu7KkBEK5B25Yl8MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=8fdf2395\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedia:RSP</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tBuqFHs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtBuqFHs.png&h=51459f24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n噉邊個決定個表上面話每一個來源可唔可靠？<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">就係一大班世界各地嘅維基人喺站務台吹水大辯論！</span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最近有幾位維基人好有心，將<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">文匯報</span></span>、<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">新华社</span></span>、<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">环球时报</span></span>、同 <span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">CGTN</span></span>（即係 CCTV 海外版）推晒上去集中討論。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedia:Reliable_sources/Noticeboard\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FWikipedia%3AReliable_sources%2FNoticeboard&d=V6cANorTbu7KkBEK5B25Yl8MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=e91e3d95\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedia:Reliable_sources/Noticeboard</a><br />\n<br />\n而家似乎呢<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"blue\">四個黨媒都會判成「假新聞」</span></span>(Publishes false or fabricated information)，<strong>將會禁絕於英文維基百科呢條咁重要嘅國際戰線</strong>！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VkoZK9S.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVkoZK9S.png&h=e1665132&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n大家睇下隊形幾齊~ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外<ins>南華早報</ins>都傾緊，暫時傾向認爲佢哋雖然奶開共但係未變晒黨媒，報新聞仲係可靠嘅。亦有人提議緊推埋 <ins>China Daily</ins> 同埋<ins>大公報</ins>上去公審 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家歡迎食花生，亦歡迎維基手足加入戰團 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過<strong>戴返頭盔先，大家等班維基手足靜靜地贏就好</strong>，唔係做開維基手足嘅巴絲麻煩唔好入去搞寸個場，維基百科好忌站外拉票 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2c10524d87fbe5efce6667b2e895fa09430b5ba","tid":2148301,"uid":359959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b97f60fe7883bd18d575ccc69aca6f3486872465","tid":2148301,"uid":363335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T00:42:19.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\">大家可能知道維基百科嘅內容需要引用「可靠來源」。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n乜嘢係維基百科嘅<strong>「可靠來源」</strong>？原來維基百科有一大個表，列舉常見嘅新聞網站有幾可靠。<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedia:RSP\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FWikipedia%3ARSP&d=V6cANorTbu7KkBEK5B25Yl8MSy0xN